  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかったよ。
ミソを接着剤代わりにするのは諦めるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fine. I'll stop trying to use
miso as a substitute for glue.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よかった。　わかってくれたんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm glad. You actually understand.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>本当によかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It really is a good thing...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>懐中時計開いて見えるのが
針じゃなくてミソだったら嫌だもんね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You probably wouldn't like opening your
pocket watch only to see miso in it
instead of the pointer, anyway.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？
べつに嫌じゃないよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? That wouldn't be bad at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そ、そう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I-Is that right...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
